As you'd know if you followed these discussions, I announced that I had
repudiated the "B" key in 1992, right after I learned of the legal
controversies surrounding PGP, and had destroyed my copy of the software.
Some "not fully informed person" brings this up regularly and I've publicly
replied equally regularly.

As to the 1993 "5C" key, that is bogus and I've issued no PGP keys since the
repudiated 9/24/1992 one.

David
